extends layout

block header

block content

    h3 Heroku Config Variables for '#{app_name}'

    p The following is a list of app/sites on Heroku. The CI Server will attempt to build 
      a site, or update a site for each branch submitted. If you want more immediate control
      of a heroku site, for testing, tweaks or debugging you can use the 'git remote add ' + git URL.
      The heroku CLI will then allow you to access app using 'heroku COMMAND --remote [remoteName]'.

    br

    .row-fluid
      .span12
        button(class="btn btn-small", onclick="alert('Coming soon...');") Add New Config Var

        br
        br

        table.table-striped.table.table-hover
         tr
          th(width="20%")
           | Name
          th(width="40%")
           | Value
          th(width="20%")

          - if (!data || data.length == 0) 
             tr
              td(colspan="5")
               | No processes started.
          - else
            each val, i in data
             tr
              td=i
              td=val
              td
               button(class="btn btn-small", onclick="alert('Coming soon...');") Remove
               | &nbsp;
               button(class="btn btn-small", onclick="alert('Coming soon...');") Edit

        a(class="btn btn-primary", href="/heroku/apps") Return to App List